==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Megalethoscope
<hw>Meg`a*leth"o*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Mega-</ets> + <ets>alethoscope</ets>.]</ety> <def>An optical
apparatus in which pictures are viewed through a large lens with
stereoptical effects. It is often combined with the
stereoscope.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Megalith</ent>⟦br⟧
